  type: 'text',\par
  admin: \{\par
    components: \{\par
      Error: '/path/to/MyCustomErrorComponent', \par
    \},\par
  \},\par
\}\par
All Error Components receive the Default Field Component Props.\par
\par
For details on how to build Custom Components themselves, see Building Custom Components.\par
\par
